{"id":139884,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/《人民日报》两年内使用完全相同的头版版面/","date":"2011-03-15T17:47:59Z","modified":"2011-03-15T17:55:41Z","title":"《人民日报》两年内使用完全相同的头版版面","content":"<p>3月14日全国政协十一届四次会议闭幕，去年同一天是全国政协十一届三次会议闭幕。非常有意思的是，《华尔街日报》比较了两年里中国共产党党报《人民日报》同一天头版新闻，发现除了三和四有差异外，两者布局甚至照片都几乎一模一样，版面差异微乎其微。当然，类似的事情在《人民日报》上并不是同一次出现。知名论坛天涯曾贴出了多年来《人民日报》两会报道的版面图片。<img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/135ff348/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E3%80%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%A4%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%B4%E7%89%88%E7%89%88%E9%9D%A2&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F03%2F15%2F1015259%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E3%80%8A%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%A4%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E7%9B%B8%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%B4%E7%89%88%E7%89%88%E9%9D%A2&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F03%2F15%2F1015259%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/97792169350/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/135ff348/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/97792169350/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/135ff348/a2.img\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=dJ_QVj0YuiQ:Auf4tGg8YKY:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=dJ_Q